      ],
      "text": "Giya was a resident of a waterfront village who met Sokka and Suki during a visit to Seashell San's House of Shells. She had an extensive knowledge of shells, and was trained in defensive combat by Suki shortly after meeting her."
    },
    {
      "body": "Sometime after the end of the ${link_0}, Giya visited Seashell San's House of Shells, and expressed interest in buying the shell of a hermit marmoset, but her offer was quickly dismissed by ${link_1}. Prior to leaving the store, Giya witnessed Suki confront San and ${link_2}. She was later approached by Suki and ${link_3}, who wanted to make sure that she was okay.",
